msgid "After rebooting"
msgstr "再起動後"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: kcm/ui/main.qml:133
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label The thing being recommended is to use the 'apply updates when rebooting' setting"
msgid "Recommended to maximize system stability"
msgstr "システムの安定性が最大化されるため推奨されます"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
